{"TopicId":175283,"ForumId":50,"TopicTitle":"Tutorial - How to link successfully to images on imgur.","CreatedByName":"NewtSoup","CreatedById":178829,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-24T23:57:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"NewtSoup","CreatedById":178829,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-24T23:57:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nGo to your imgur account and upload the image you want to display to an album - make a note of the file extension - whether it\u0027s png, jpg, etc.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGo to the image and click on the \u0022copy\u0022 button next to the link:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022mMryc8H.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022503\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/mMryc8H.png\u0022 width=\u0022735\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nNow go back to your forum post and click on the \u0022Insert Other Media\u0022 and choose insert Image from URL\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022aFzqQ4H.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022200\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/aFzqQ4H.png\u0022 width=\u0022268\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThis brings up the following window:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022mYHTpkM.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022213\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/mYHTpkM.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPaste the Copied URL into this box but do not click on \u0022Insert into post\u0022 yet - the URL is not complete it will\u00A0 look something like \u0022https://imgur.com/xWhY2cH\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nNow at the end of the URL\u00A0add the dot \u0022.\u0022 and the file extension of the original image for example \u0022png\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022at51ZCk.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022215\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/at51ZCk.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nNow you can click Insert into Post and you have your\u00A0lovely image posted - Tada:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xWhY2cH.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/xWhY2cH.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-24T23:58:16Z\u0022 title=\u002205/24/2018 11:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 24, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by NewtSoup\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-25T00:07:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see how it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NewtSoup","CreatedById":178829,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-25T00:13:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/Ofz01\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAlbum Ofz01 will appear when post is submitted\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlbum Linking doesn\u0027t work - interestingly that album code doesn\u0027t even go to one of my albums even though I copied it from the embed code for\u00A0one of my KSP albums\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022179753\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Geonovast\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0lol I hadn\u0027t seen you had almost exactly the same thing in your sig \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-25T00:16:03Z\u0022 title=\u002205/25/2018 12:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 25, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by NewtSoup\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-25T01:08:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstead of using the copy button, you can also right-click the picture and use the \u0022Copy Image Location\u0022 option to get a link already including the file extension \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}